ung bleiben dabei eng verknüpft mit den Komplexen Rüstungsbeschaffung, technologische Entwicklung und materielle Einsatzbereitschaft. Hochrangige Zeitzeugen vertiefen diese Einsichten aus ihrem Miterleben in den fliegenden Verbänden, der Flugabwehrtruppe und der Logistik.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aEuropexHistory. 4aBundeswehr. 4aDeutschland. 4aMilitärgeschichte. 4aNATO. 4aZeitgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aKlatte, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKleppien, Axel B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrüger, Dieter, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKrüger, Dieter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLemke, Bernd, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPacholke, Siegfried, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRebhan, Heinz, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRebhan, Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aScheibe, Klaus-Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmidt, Wolfgang, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aSchmidt, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchwenke, Winfried, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 avon der Felsen, Hillrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978348657973440uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348671188